---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Card } from '../components/Card';
---

<Layout title="Case Studies — Ansh Bhatt">
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-h3 text-muted mb-3">Case Studies</p>
      <h1 class="text-h1 text-ink mb-6">Real Outcomes</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted">
        Real outcomes from real constraints.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <Card client:load variant="soft">
          <p class="text-h3 text-pine mb-3">Series A SaaS Startup</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink mb-4">GTM acceleration post-seed</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-muted">
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-ink">Constraint:</span> Unclear product-market fit signals + hiring freeze.
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-ink">Intervention:</span> 6-week diagnostic, customer interview synthesis, revised positioning, hire sequencing plan.
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-ink">Result:</span> 3x pipeline growth in 90 days.
            </div>
          </div>
        </Card>

        <Card client:load variant="soft">
          <p class="text-h3 text-pine mb-3">Fintech Scale-up</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink mb-4">Regulatory pathway + ops buildout</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-muted">
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-ink">Constraint:</span> Unclear licensing roadmap. Ops stretched across 3 vendors.
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-ink">Intervention:</span> Legal bench mapped pathway. Ops audit + integration plan.
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-ink">Result:</span> License issued in 8 weeks. 30% ops cost reduction.
            </div>
          </div>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-soft">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-muted mb-4">Every engagement is custom. Each produces different outputs—but all follow the same framework: clear diagnosis, explicit options, and rigorous execution.</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted">For confidentiality reasons, most case studies stay private. Ask me directly during an initial call.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
